title: 【1.9】命令无效
author: 彪悍的新手
txt_content:
嗯之前弄好了命令成功了然后手贱破坏了命令方块QAQ
现在怎么都弄不回来了。
为什么打死召唤出来的僵尸无法掉落按钮
/summon Zombie ~ ~ ~ {Attributes:[{Name:generic.maxHealth,Base:30}],HandDropChances:[0:1f,1:1f],HandItems:[0:{id:"minecraft:wooden_button"},1:{}]}复制代码

replies.author: End-Enderman
replies.txt_content: LZ你没输入按钮的数量...比如/summon Zombie ~ ~ ~ {Attributes:[{Name:generic.maxHealth,Base:30}],HandDropChances:[0:1.0f,1:1.0f],HandItems:[0:{id:"minecraft:wooden_button",Count:1b},1:{}]}复制代码
